Theme Song Finalist Information (with lyrical connection)

Final Song Standing: Official Among Us In Real Life


Lyrics (excerpt):
Gotta find the imposter as they try to sabotage
Who can we trust in this Among Us entourage?

Heard a sound, turned around, looking up, looking down
Then I find a dead body!
Connection:
In these few lines, the song talks about the uncertainty of the environment and the unexcepted events. This, in turn, can be reflected in my life as I (and possibly you) experience life and do not know for sure what will happen in the future. This can also connect to my mission statment because in the song, the characters have to adapt and endure challenges (murderer, sabotages), and to give and to then recieve their best product (do tasks, and win the game).
